overview: He's back, and he has even more clientele than last time. Just how does he do it? He's nothing more than a creepy massage guy, right? Wrong! He's down to Earth, and he really gets women. He knows the whole pillow-talk routine, so he gets it out of the way in the beginning, that way there's nothing to talk about after he blows his load across their face and his massage table!
title: Massage Creep 7
